    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone looking for a solid value. The engine and transmission are functioning correctly, though the car would benefit from a routine tune-up and new brake pads in the near future. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable door dings, some paint fading on the hood, and a small crack in the rear bumper plastic. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant staining on the driver's seat and some wear on the steering wheel. All electronics work, including the AC, although the radio display is occasionally dim. It is a dependable car that reflects its mileage and age honestly.",
