    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, she looks like she just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been babied since day one\u2014always garaged, smoke-free, and not a single scratch or ding to be found. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You won't find another one in this kind of shape! Come take a look and see for yourself!",
